Package semsim.annotation

Class Annotation

java.lang.Object
semsim.annotation.Annotation
Direct Known Subclasses:
ReferenceOntologyAnnotation
public class Annotation
extends java.lang.Object
A SemSim annotation provides additional information about a SemSim model or one of its elements. Annotations can be used to define the physical meaning of a SemSim model or model element, identify model authors, link a model to its PubMed ID, etc.
